                                    <sic>Geschicthe</sic>
                                    <corr>Literatur</corr>
                                </choice>
                            </title>, 227.</bibl>
                        <bibl>W. Gesenius, <title rend="italic">De Bar Alio et Bar Bahlulo,
                                lexicographis Syro-Arabicis ineditis, commentatio litteraria
                                philologica</title>, vol. 1 (1834), 7–8.</bibl>
                        <bibl>Duval, <title rend="italic">La littérature syriaque</title>, 271–2 and
                            297.</bibl>
                        <bibl>Graf, <title rend="italic">GCAL</title>, vol. 2, 110.</bibl>
                        <bibl>H.  Putman, <title rend="italic">L’Eglise et l’Islam sous Timothée I
                                (780–823)</title> (1975), 35, 98–101, passim.</bibl>
                        <bibl>M. Ullmann, <title rend="italic">Die Medizin im Islam</title> (1970),
                            109.</bibl>
                        <bibl>Wright, <title rend="italic">Short history of Syriac
                                literature</title>, 214–5.</bibl>
                    </listBibl>
                </div>
                <byline>
                    <persName>
                  <forename>Aaron M.</forename> 
                  <surname>Butts</surname>
               </persName>
                </byline>
